name: Labyrinth (itch) (Fontys Game Design & Technology)
description:
Labyrinth (itch) (Fontys Game Design & Technology) is an adventure, puzzle and platformer game developed by Fontys Game Design & Technology. It was originally released in 2021.
Labyrinth (itch) (Fontys Game Design & Technology) is available on Web. The game is sold via itch.io.
